# Top-level nav order (awesome-pages). `...` auto-appends any unlisted page, so
# adding a new top-level doc needs no edit here. Titles are pinned only where they
# must differ from the page's H1 (Home, Walkthrough); the rest use their heading.
nav:
  - Home: index.md
  - getting-started.md
  - operations.md
  - Walkthrough: walkthrough.md
  - concepts.md
  - reference
  - ...
  - Design docs ↗: https://github.com/smith153/ShorewallNF/tree/master/docs
